{"tid":1848960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真就算戴左口罩同眼鏡都仲有機會中招....","createTime":"2020-01-28T18:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T10:53:16.000Z","uid":15259,"like":629,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"a89090073ca7dc9c8c9a1a7ad6734950de3012c4","tid":1848960,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:20:09.000Z","msg":"但我哋仲可以做多層保護呀！依家我地要防既係飛沫，即使戴左口罩都仲有機會比飛沫入眼或者經口罩既空隙入左鼻或口<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54OGe9E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54OGe9E.jpg&h=d4ae4861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然我地無可能著到好似上面呢張圖咁樣出街，但係我地可以買一頂<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">太陽帽</span></span></strong></span>做多一層<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">防護</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfB8ECr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfB8ECr.jpg&h=1d96fad5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n太陽帽成本低，保護性高，方便，重點係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>遮到全塊面</strong></span></span>，咁當然係絕對有可能起個罩既下面飛D飛沫上黎，但用左呢頂帽已經大大阻隔左飛沫直接噴向面部既機會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般黎講，12蚊店/AEON/千色/普通運動舖都會有，價錢由12蚊至200蚊不等，價錢視乎防UV程度/不同牌子而定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地首要目的係防止飛沫入眼、鼻、口，所以其實防幾多UV唔太重點，重點係個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">表面夠大就得</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清潔方面(用後必做)</span></span></strong><br />\n每次用完收之前可以用<span style=\"color: gold;\">75%消毒火酒</span>或者<span style=\"color: gold;\">消毒洗手液</span>清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁樣理論上可以確保到收返埋時候個表面唔會整污穢其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n覺得適合既麻煩各位巴絲打推上去比更多巴絲睇，謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75243f74a6fe4e014da8712cebdad96f761138e","tid":1848960,"uid":140218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"ffdc6aef839f5a8f749097f31be2bff108905581","tid":1848960,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:23:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ee1d6517d6942237a5c100001e74a85756ea1f0","tid":1848960,"uid":256620,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"[行動]129黎明行動 召喚嘔吐師-<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1848751/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1848751/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjbXxpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjbXxpE.jpg&h=80c8210c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56795e2ce90165b1710adca1ea10b71f81781975","tid":1848960,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:30:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"125dd95e02ccd1e625ab52e324701281918fcbf2","tid":1848960,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:31:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f317849d6d946afc4ad3a197a8e0f5f97f5ec114","tid":1848960,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"想搵搵唔倒"},{"pid":"14e5f685189ae2ade790bc34511eb21fdd7e828d","tid":1848960,"uid":184370,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"帶個水樽係頭到"},{"pid":"5a32fcb70de05782985485a6c7cb5f81d589d252","tid":1848960,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14e5f685189ae2ade790bc34511eb21fdd7e828d","tid":1848960,"uid":184370,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"帶個水樽係頭到"},"citedBy":0,